Caja  Madrid , a shareholder of  NH
Hoteles SA , will force Gabriele Burgio to will step down as
chairman of the Spanish hotelier,  El Confidencial  reported.  NH Hoteles will hold a board meeting today to discuss the
issue, El Confidencial said, citing unidentified people with
knowledge of the matter.  Spokesmen for Caja Madrid and NH Hoteles both declined to
comment on the report when contacted by Bloomberg News.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharon Smyth in Madrid at 
 ssmyth2@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Blackman at 
 ablackman@bloomberg.net . 